UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Dendrite makes another invisible gesture in the air above him as you approach. Another aura of power comes over him. and he smiles ever so slightly.$B$B"I sense wisdom in you, young one, that was not present when we first met. You gaze upon me with strength and knowing intent, though this intent is yet not focused. You will now learn to focus your strength and adopt the nature of the bear into your work."' WHERE entry=5929;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Dendrite makes another invisible gesture in the air above him as you approach. Another aura of power comes over him. and he smiles ever so slightly.$B$B"I sense wisdom in you, young one, that was not present when we first met. You gaze upon me with strength and knowing intent, though this intent is yet not focused. You will now learn to focus your strength and adopt the nature of the bear into your work."' WHERE entry=5930;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Welcome back, $N. I sense that your first meeting with the Great Bear Spirit is the same as it is with all druids when they first start down the path of the Claw... a little bewildering, but very intense. I know it was that way with me.$B$BThe Great Bear Spirit has been a part of Azeroth as long as Azeroth has existed in the heavens. We have come to rely on its wisdom and its power to fuel our purpose. Now, the time has now come for your first test of this purpose. Listen closely...' WHERE entry=5931;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Welcome back, $N. I sense that your first meeting with the Great Bear Spirit is the same as it is with all druids when they first start down the path of the Claw... a little bewildering, but very intense. I know it was that way with me.$B$BThe Great Bear Spirit has been a part of Azeroth as long as Azeroth has existed in the heavens. We tauren listen closely to such spirits, and we all prosper from its purpose. Now, the time has now come for your first test of this purpose. Listen closely...' WHERE entry=5932;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah yes, there they are. Together they weave a powerful spell, one that will raise the spirits of Darrowshire.$B$BWith that spell, and with a little luck, we can save Joseph Redpath!' WHERE entry=5941;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The key fits the lock, and the chest opens...' WHERE entry=5942;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Not sure it\'s a prosperous proposition to be paying so much money to protect the Gizelton Caravan. Cork and Rigger only make one gold piece a week, but as long as they keep paying for my kodos I can care less how they run their business.' WHERE entry=5943;
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='You know, if that caravan were to ever disappear I would be ruined! You\'re not the bearer of bad news about the caravan, are you?$B$B<Smeed wipes his brow.>$B$BThank the goddess of greed!' WHERE entry=5943;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The death of my son at the hands of these monsters will not pass without incident. Take solace in knowing that the Order is reborn.$B$BI now take my place as Highlord of the new Order of the Silver Hand.$B$BThese possessions of my past - they are all that I have to offer for all that you have done. Please, take these as a symbol of my gratitude; all have served me well over the years.$B$BMay we meet again, in better times, and reminisce of days long past... battles hard fought... dreams redeemed.' WHERE entry=5944;
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='<Tirion regains his composure.>' WHERE entry=5944;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Surely the Dark Lady does not believe you worthy to meet her champion. You are here to feed my hounds, yes? There could be no other reason for this interruption.' WHERE entry=5961;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent, $N. Your determination has been duly noted.' WHERE entry=5981;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You have finally taken your large step into a much larger world, $N. I sense the teaching of the Great Bear Spirit within you, and I sense that you have received the strength that Lunaclaw possessed.$B$BThere are no further obstacles in your way... let me now teach you what it means to be a Druid of the Claw!' WHERE entry=6001;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You have finally taken your large step into a much larger world, $N. I sense the teaching of the Great Bear Spirit within you, and I sense that you have received the strength that Lunaclaw possessed.$B$BThere are no further obstacles in your way... let me now teach you what it means to be a Druid of the Claw!' WHERE entry=6002;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, $N. I\'m amazed you dealt with them so quickly. Thank you.$B$BI have yet to meet anyone that approves of the Scarlet Crusade and their methods. I believe in the Light as much as anyone else in Stormwind, but they\'ve demonstrated that they only want to kill anyone not loyal to their movement... even innocents.' WHERE entry=6004;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Great, you got him!  And I hope you taught his gang a lesson too!' WHERE entry=6021;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Disappointing. I was hoping that I\'d be feeding you to my hounds, instead.$B$B<Nathanos sighs.>$B$BWell, at least you they\'ll have something to eat.' WHERE entry=6022;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you, $N. You\'ve been more help than I could have hoped for. The air here just seems to suck my will. I feel tired, and I can tell I\'m not getting any better the longer I\'m here.$B$BI\'m not really sure how I\'m going to infiltrate Hearthglen itself and report on how strong the Scarlet Crusade\'s presence is.$B$BBut that\'s another matter, before you leave, here, take this... as payment for your help. Thank you again.' WHERE entry=6023;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Hameya\'s chest is opened!!' WHERE entry=6024;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve done it, $N! Thank you!$B$BI\'ll return to Elling... I mean Stormwind as soon as I can. Here, take this coin, it\'s the least I can do for you. You\'re a credit to your people, $N. Thank you and good luck.' WHERE entry=6025;
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='It\'s a dangerous task, $N. I envy your courage.' WHERE entry=6025;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I can pay you half up front and half when the job is done.' WHERE entry=6026;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The long lost Book of the Ancients! I will ensure this book is passed on to the high council. You\'ve done well today, and for that you are to be thanked... as a hero should be thanked!$B$B' WHERE entry=6027;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Very resourceful, Gregor is. He\'s been dealing with the Steamwheedle Cartel for some time now, and has become an expert on the "art" of goblin negotiations. Though it\'s true that the goblins\' primary loyalties lie with those who have the largest coin purses, they also know and respect the value of diplomacy. If anything, it provides them with repeat customers...$B$BAt any rate, the Argent Dawn acknowledges you for your effort. Please have this, with our thanks.' WHERE entry=6028;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Resourceful for a human, Gregor is.  He\'s been dealing with the Steamwheedle Cartel for some time now, and has become an expert on the "art" of goblin negotiations.  Though it\'s true that the goblins\' primary loyalties lie with those who have the largest coin purses, they also know and respect the value of diplomacy.  If anything, it provides them with repeat customers...$B$BAt any rate, the Argent Dawn acknowledges you for your effort.  Please have this, with our thanks.' WHERE entry=6029;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This... this is a very special book you have brought me. I\'d like to tell you that "special" in this case means "unique and quite possibly illuminating", but that remains to be seen.$B$B"Ooooooo?" Who in their right mind thinks this up?$B$BWell now, I\'ve heard of this Umbranse that Gregor spoke of, so this isn\'t without merit. I\'ll do my best to decipher it. As for you... please, have this - courtesy of the Argent Dawn. While you are here, perhaps there are some other things you can aid us with.' WHERE entry=6030;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, you brought the cloth.  Such fine material it is!$B$BThank you, $N.  You are a true friend.  Please accept this in exchange.' WHERE entry=6031;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, very good. This mooncloth will be used for garments sacred to our people. Thank you, $N. Now I will train you.' WHERE entry=6032;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'re much darker than I remember. You got that look going for you; the look that says, \'I\'ve been charred by a high explosive bomb.\'$B$B<Smokey laughs.>$B$BAnyhow! Here\'s your cut of the loot. I\'ve thrown in a little something extra to help soothe the burns.' WHERE entry=6041;
