UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Captain Shatterskull roars in triumph.>$B$BHow much more can they withstand? How many more Alliance filth must perish at the hands of the Horde for them to retreat? Only time will tell, $R.' WHERE entry=7874;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Captain Shatterskull roars in triumph.>$B$BHow much more can they withstand? How many more Alliance filth must perish at the hands of the Horde for them to retreat? Only time will tell, $R.' WHERE entry=7875;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Captain Shatterskull roars in triumph.>$B$BHow much more can they withstand? How many more Alliance filth must perish at the hands of the Horde for them to retreat? Only time will tell, $R.' WHERE entry=7876;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You open the chest to find...' WHERE entry=7877;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you, $N.  These are quite well made.  The craftsmanship is top notch!  Here is a Darkmoon Faire ticket... enjoy, sir.' WHERE entry=7881;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, you brought the jerkins.  Splendid.  What animal\'s skin did you use to make these, may I ask?  The stitch-work is very well done, and the texture of the leather has a rugged style to it.  I can tell you are a craftsman of skill!$B$BThank you, $N, and here are your tickets.' WHERE entry=7882;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Oh dear, these are quite large!! I can\'t imagine finding a gnome that would fit snuggly into them, but not to worry - if the gnome we find is not big enough, I can make adjustments to his costume.$B$BMany thanks, $N. Here are the tickets I promised you.' WHERE entry=7883;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Great, you made them!  These will do nicely... I just hope I won\'t be the one to clean the crocolisk cage when the time comes.  Those beasts can be rather beastly, don\'t you think?$B$BHere are your tickets, $N.  Enjoy them, and enjoy your stay at the Darkmoon Faire!' WHERE entry=7884;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Great! This will work great! I just noticed a rip in a tent over yonder, and one of these armor kits is just what I need to patch it up!$B$BThank you very much, $N. These armor kits will save us a ton in repair costs. Here are your tickets - you deserve them!' WHERE entry=7885;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='You have proven your value to our efforts in Warsong Gulch. Continue to aid the cause and bring me more talismans of merit. Do this, and you will earn even more of our trust.',objectives_loc2='You obtained a Silverwing Talisman of Merit for your last task, talk to me again, and you gain your reward.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you, $N. Your exploits in Warsong Gulch ring throughout Ashenvale Forest.' WHERE entry=7886;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='You have proven your value to our efforts in Warsong Gulch. Continue to aid the cause and bring me more talismans of merit. Do this, and you will earn even more of our trust.',objectives_loc2='You obtained a Silverwing Talisman of Merit for your last task, talk to me again, and you gain your reward.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you, $N. Your exploits in Warsong Gulch ring throughout Ashenvale Forest.' WHERE entry=7887;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='You have proven your value to our efforts in Warsong Gulch. Continue to aid the cause and bring me more talismans of merit. Do this, and you will earn even more of our trust.',objectives_loc2='You obtained a Silverwing Talisman of Merit for your last task, talk to me again, and you gain your reward.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you, $N. Your exploits in Warsong Gulch ring throughout Ashenvale Forest.' WHERE entry=7888;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Great! These will work great! They\'re not too heavy, but not too light either. They\'re perfect for building muscle mass!$B$BThanks much, $N. Here\'s your Darkmoon Faire ticket!' WHERE entry=7889;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You brought the stones! And they\'re heavy! I can already feel my muscles getting bigger. Thanks $N!$B$BHere, take these tickets, and be sure not to eat too many sweets while your at the faire. A big strong $C like you needs to keep himself in fighting shape!' WHERE entry=7890;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thanks much, $N. Here\'s your Darkmoon Faire tickets!' WHERE entry=7891;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thanks much, $N. Here\'s your Darkmoon Faire tickets!' WHERE entry=7892;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thanks much, $N. Here\'s your Darkmoon Faire tickets!' WHERE entry=7893;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Aha! The modulators! Superb!$B$BI can\'t tell you exactly what we\'re building, but these will be invaluable for its construction. I am in your debt, Grimling, but please, take this Darkmoon Faire ticket as a token of my appreciation.' WHERE entry=7894;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You brought the gizmos! Wonderful! Even now I can hear their buzzing, whirring chorus in my mind! Oh, when this booth is ready it will be the wonder of the world, mark me! $B$BHere are your tickets, $N. And please enjoy your stay at the Faire!' WHERE entry=7895;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You brought the fireworks. Wonderful work, $N! I can\'t wait to light these and tell the world that my booth is ready to go! I must still wait, quite a long time I\'m afraid, but... I\'ll be ready when I\'m ready, yes?$B$BHere are the tickets, $N. Enjoy yourself!' WHERE entry=7896;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you! Now I can get to fixing things.$B$BIt\'s going to take a lot of repair kits and a lot of late nights to get everything in working order. Sometimes I think it\'d be better to get back to my roots and restart my career as a headhunter, but... the Faire has been good to me.$B$BTake these tickets, $N, and have fun!' WHERE entry=7897;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, thank you, $N! Yebb will enjoy these widgets. I don\'t know what he has planned for them, but Yebb\'s a clever little gnome. He\'s clever, and maybe a little devious....$B$BIf only he liked the taste of humanoid flesh... he\'d make a great troll!$B$BHere, $N. A deal\'s a deal, and these tickets are yours.' WHERE entry=7898;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Great, you got them! We can use these to make toys and baubles, and those will attract more people to the Faire!$B$BHere\'s your ticket, $N. You earned it!' WHERE entry=7899;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Nice pelts, $N! I\'ll get someone to sew these into a bunch of plush toys. With a little stuffing and some paint, I think they\'ll be the envy of children across Azeroth!$B$BTickets? Ah yes, your payment!$B$BHere they are!' WHERE entry=7900;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, $N! These tails will make great prizes for our visitors, and that means happy visitors... who talk to their friends and bring more visitors!$B$BHere are your tickets! Have a good time at the Darkmoon Faire... and don\'t forget to tell your friends about us!' WHERE entry=7901;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, the plumes! They are amazing, don\'t you think! It would be easy to spark one\'s imaginations with such beauties!$B$BYou do such charitable work, $N. The smiles on our visitors\' faces when they see the show is a grand payment indeed, but please take these tickets as well.' WHERE entry=7902;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Great!  You got the eyes!  I hope hunting those bats was frightening for you, because if it scared a brave $C like yourself, then those eyes will certainly scare our Faire visitors.$B$BTake these tickets, $N, and thank you for your service.' WHERE entry=7903;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Welcome to the Darkmoon Faire!  This voucher is good for FIVE, yes, FIVE prize tickets!$B$BWhen you accumulate prize tickets, you\'ll want to speak to me about redeeming them for valuable prizes.  The more tickets you get, the more prizes you can win.  Huzzah!' WHERE entry=7905;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well this explains a lot. If you ever find a way into Ahn\'Qiraj, keep an eye out for ol\' Brann. I\'m afraid that he\'ll be powerless without his monkey.' WHERE entry=7907;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='You have proven your value to our efforts in Warsong Gulch. Continue to aid the cause and bring me more talismans of merit. Do this, and you will earn even more of our trust.',objectives_loc2='You obtained a Silverwing Talisman of Merit for your last task, talk to me again, and you gain your reward.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you, $N. Your exploits in Warsong Gulch ring throughout Ashenvale Forest.' WHERE entry=7921;
