UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Hurry up and turn those in if you want to be declared the Master Angler!  I have been standing around here for HOURS with nothing to eat!   Hand those suckers over!' WHERE entry=8193;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This deal works for me if it works for you!' WHERE entry=8194;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='I seek the Paragons of Power known as the Coins of the Tribes.  They are the currency used by the various denizens of Zul\'Gurub, and each is imbued with subtle but powerful mojo.$B$BThere are nine distinct kinds to be found.  Some are sought after by my compatriots for various armors they offer Zandalar heroes.  Should you have any extra, I will trade you one of our Honor Tokens for a set of three.  You may use the Tokens with Rin\'wosho the Trader; he offers our heroes special items for them.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!' WHERE entry=8195;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='A fair trade, my friend - please enjoy the luscious fruits of the South Seas, with the tribe\'s blessing.' WHERE entry=8196;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You gained the heads!  You have halted the plundering of our gods\' power, and weakened Hakkar!$B$BYour actions are truly heroic, $N.  May the heads of these troll thralls plead to you for mercy long after their blood chills.' WHERE entry=8201;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='*Whir* $B$B Identification of Keefer\'s Angelfish complete. $B$B Your Reward is now available. $B$B *click-click* *Bzzzz*' WHERE entry=8221;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Great job, $N!  Thanks a lot!  I\'m going to make paint from this blood and turn all kinds of cheap junk into glowing treasure!$B$BHere are your tickets, and thanks again!' WHERE entry=8222;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thanks again, $N.  Here are your tickets!' WHERE entry=8223;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='*Whir* $B$B Identification of Dezian Queenfish complete. $B$B Your Reward is now available. $B$B *click-click* *Bzzzz*' WHERE entry=8224;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Why, you found my favorite measuring tape! I love this tape! I measured some of the biggest fish I ever caught with it...$B$BBut, I lost this tape in Zul\'Gurub... you\'ve been to Zul\'Gurub? Did you see the fabled Gahz\'ranka?$B$BWell... do you want to catch him?' WHERE entry=8227;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='There be a Fishin Contest in Booty Bay this Sunday! Here are the rules for ya!' WHERE entry=8228;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='There is a Fishing Contest in Booty Bay this Sunday! Here are the rules for you!' WHERE entry=8229;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The wavethrashers are not easily defeated, even more so in their watery environment.$B$BYou have proven yourself ready to hunt even deadlier prey.' WHERE entry=8231;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You have learned the old ways, $N, and for that I offer you a gift from my days as a hunter.' WHERE entry=8232;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Welcome, welcome, welcome!  Please, $N, have a seat and discuss a simple matter with me.$B$BYou see, $N, I\'ve recently lost something dear to me, and to put it bluntly, I want it back at all costs.  There\'s something in it for you, don\'t worry about that!  Oh yes, something very nice.$B$BNow, what say you $N... are you up for some adventure?' WHERE entry=8233;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I see you have Lord Ravenholdt\'s bag. Why didn\'t you say so, boy?' WHERE entry=8234;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='It looks like you picked up some of the better fragments. Perhaps you aren\'t worthless after all.' WHERE entry=8235;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The key! I thought it lost forever. Please, take an enchanted garment from my stores -- they are reserved for rogues of exceptional skill and loyalty. It should be known that $N is not to be trifled with!$B$B<Jorach opens the bag and is bathed by a golden glow from within. His eyes widen and he stares...>' WHERE entry=8236;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='I seek the Paragons of Power known as the Coins of the Tribes.  They are the currency used by the various denizens of Zul\'Gurub, and each is imbued with subtle but powerful mojo.$B$BThere are nine distinct kinds to be found.  Some are sought after by my compatriots for various armors they offer Zandalar heroes.  Should you have any extra, I will trade you one of our Honor Tokens for a set of three.  You may use the Tokens with Rin\'wosho the Trader; he offers our heroes special items for them.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!' WHERE entry=8238;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='I seek the Paragons of Power known as the Coins of the Tribes.  They are the currency used by the various denizens of Zul\'Gurub, and each is imbued with subtle but powerful mojo.$B$BThere are nine distinct kinds to be found.  Some are sought after by my compatriots for various armors they offer Zandalar heroes.  Should you have any extra, I will trade you one of our Honor Tokens for a set of three.  You may use the Tokens with Rin\'wosho the Trader; he offers our heroes special items for them.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!' WHERE entry=8239;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent... each bijou we wrest away from the Blood God\'s minions is one step closer we all are to finally defeating them once and for all.  You bring honor to the Zandalar - and yourself - through your noble actions.$B$BRemember $N, you may always destroy the bijous you find in Zul\'Gurub at the altar.  For each one, you will gain recognition and an Honor Token!  Just remember to have an open space in your inventory if you don\'t have one of the tokens already.' WHERE entry=8240;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='Let\'s not waste more of my precious time with jibber jabber, $R. It\'s time to focus on replenishing our dwindling fiery flux supply.$B$BWhat I\'m gonna need from you is the following:$B$B*Incendosaur scales.$B$B*Iron bars.$B$B*Coal.$B$BI\'ll take all that you can offer!$B$BAnd you\'ll do it fast if you wanna get in good with the Brotherhood.',offerrewardtext_loc2='There\'s always room for more fiery flux, junior. Keep it comin\'... unless I tell you to stop.' WHERE entry=8241;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='Let\'s not waste more of my precious time with jibber jabber, $R. It\'s time to focus on replenishing our dwindling fiery flux supply.$B$BWhat I\'m gonna need from you is the following:$B$B*Incendosaur scales.$B$B*Heavy Leather.$B$B*Coal.$B$BI\'ll take all that you can offer!$B$BAnd you\'ll do it fast if you wanna get in good with the Brotherhood.',offerrewardtext_loc2='There\'s always room for more fiery flux, junior. Keep it comin\'... unless I tell you to stop.' WHERE entry=8242;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='A fair trade, my friend - please enjoy the blessings of Zanza with our compliments!' WHERE entry=8243;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='A fair trade, my friend - please accept your signet with the blessing of the tribe!' WHERE entry=8246;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='May these knives find a place in someone\'s heart.$B$BLiterally.' WHERE entry=8249;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Sanath sneers at you.>$B$BArchmage Xylem awaits your arrival.' WHERE entry=8250;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, $N!  It never ceases to amaze me how persuasive a volley of arcane missiles can be.' WHERE entry=8251;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This is a superb specimen of coral, $N.  Your skills are unquestionably precise and deadly.$B$BDo not think your efforts have gone unnoticed.  Perhaps you are worthy of a true test of your skill...' WHERE entry=8252;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Incredible.  The shard has grown as it absorbed the drake\'s energy over the long years.$B$BThere is no more I can ask of you now.  My full ability to forge the arcane has returned with this shard.  My first creation is yours, $N, and you have but to choose...' WHERE entry=8253;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='It is good the divine path has led you to us, $N. Your beliefs do not interfere with the tasks involved in creating this salve.$B$BYou see, the courser is sacred to the Cenarion Circle, and killing them for any reason, no matter how necessary, weakens their spirit.' WHERE entry=8255;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I cannot say I\'m pleased to receive such a wretched substance, but it is a necessary evil. Thank you, $N.' WHERE entry=8256;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You have slain Morphaz and carried his blood to us... I can hardly believe this good news!$B$BWe will combine the ingredients at once and begin healing the trees and creatures of Felwood. It will take a lifetime to undo what has happened here, but you have given us the means to do it.' WHERE entry=8257;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This is a victory to savor, $N! The demise of Darkreaver should restore the fragile fetters that anchor the spirit realm.$B$BYou have far exceeded what was asked of you, even when you had no notion of reward or compensation. You are truly a $C of worth, my friend.$B$BI know that acting to preserve the spirit realm should be thanks enough, but please - accept this simple gift with my thanks.' WHERE entry=8258;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Arathi Basin. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Basin, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Honored with us, and bandages when you are Revered.' WHERE entry=8260;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Arathi Basin. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Basin, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Honored with us, and bandages when you are Revered.' WHERE entry=8261;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Arathi Basin. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Basin, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Honored with us, and bandages when you are Revered.' WHERE entry=8262;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Arathi Basin. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Basin, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Honored with us, and bandages when you are Revered.' WHERE entry=8263;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Arathi Basin. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Basin, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Honored with us, and bandages when you are Revered.' WHERE entry=8264;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Arathi Basin. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Basin, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Honored with us, and bandages when you are Revered.' WHERE entry=8265;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='I understand that it can be difficult at times to come out on top in Warsong Gulch. Still, your effort on our behalf - even when victory is not achieved - is important.$B$BShould you complete one of the trials inside Warsong Gulch and not achieve victory, you will still receive a Ribbons of Sacrifice. Bring it to me so that the Outriders may reward you for acting on our behalf... even if you weren\'t able to win this time.',objectives_loc2='Bring the Ribbons of Sacrifice to Captain Shatterskull so that the Outriders may reward you for acting on our behalf.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Well, you did not flee in the face of defeat. You stood your ground, $N, and when it comes right down to it, that is what makes for a true hero. No doubt you will win next time... but nonetheless we thank you for your effort.' WHERE entry=8266;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='I understand that it can be difficult at times to come out on top in Warsong Gulch. Still, your effort on our behalf - even when victory is not achieved - is important.$B$BShould you complete one of the trials inside Warsong Gulch and not achieve victory, you will still receive a Ribbons of Sacrifice. Bring it to me so that the Outriders may reward you for acting on our behalf... even if you weren\'t able to win this time.',objectives_loc2='Bring the Ribbons of Sacrifice to Captain Shatterskull so that the Outriders may reward you for acting on our behalf.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Well, you did not flee in the face of defeat. You stood your ground, $N, and when it comes right down to it, that is what makes for a true hero. No doubt you will win next time... but nonetheless we thank you for your effort.' WHERE entry=8267;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='I understand that it can be difficult at times to come out on top in Warsong Gulch. Still, your effort on our behalf - even when victory is not achieved - is important.$B$BShould you complete one of the trials inside Warsong Gulch and not achieve victory, you will still receive a Ribbons of Sacrifice. Bring it to me so that the Sentinels may reward you for acting on our behalf... even if you weren\'t able to win this time.',objectives_loc2='Bring the Ribbons of Sacrifice to Sentinel Farsong so that the Sentinels may reward you for acting on our behalf.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Well, you did not flee in the face of defeat. You stood your ground, $N, and when it comes right down to it, that is what makes for a true hero. No doubt you will win next time... but nonetheless we thank you for your effort.' WHERE entry=8268;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='I understand that it can be difficult at times to come out on top in Warsong Gulch. Still, your effort on our behalf - even when victory is not achieved - is important.$B$BShould you complete one of the trials inside Warsong Gulch and not achieve victory, you will still receive a Ribbons of Sacrifice. Bring it to me so that the Sentinels may reward you for acting on our behalf... even if you weren\'t able to win this time.',objectives_loc2='Bring the Ribbons of Sacrifice to Sentinel Farsong so that the Sentinels may reward you for acting on our behalf.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Well, you did not flee in the face of defeat. You stood your ground, $N, and when it comes right down to it, that is what makes for a true hero. No doubt you will win next time... but nonetheless we thank you for your effort.' WHERE entry=8269;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Now isn\'t this interesting? You say you found this tablet on a small, deserted island at The Overlook Cliffs in The Hinterlands, $C? Very interesting indeed. <Oran carefully puts the tablet away and rubs her hands together.>$B$BI thank you for your efforts in this matter. Our Dark Lady shall be very pleased with this discovery. Here, allow me to reward you proportionately.' WHERE entry=8273;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent, a new recruit answering the call to arms against the silithid. Welcome to Cenarion Hold, $C. I am pleased to see the words of our emissaries are reaching heroes of your caliber. You will find no shortage of opportunities to help us in our efforts here and I expect you\'ll quickly prove to be a valuable ally to our cause.' WHERE entry=8275;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent, a new recruit answering the call to arms against the silithid. Welcome to Cenarion Hold, $C. I am pleased to see the words of our emissaries are reaching heroes of your caliber. You will find no shortage of opportunities to help us in our efforts here and I expect you\'ll quickly prove to be a valuable ally to our cause.' WHERE entry=8276;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Cross your fingers, friend!  Here\'s to hoping we can save Noggle!' WHERE entry=8277;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yes!  It seems to be working, Noggle is coming to.  We owe ya big time!' WHERE entry=8278;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yes! These are the parts to the book!  Let\'s get started then, $N.$B$BSwap every third word with words from the second chapter... then swap every other word with words from the first chapter...  Wait, did I get that backwards?' WHERE entry=8279;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You have my sincere gratitude.  Your efforts in helping Cenarion Hold have shown true courage.' WHERE entry=8280;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent!  You\'ve proven to be a valuable ally in preparing for the war against the silithid.' WHERE entry=8281;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yes!  You brought my satchel back.  And my rare reagents are all here!  I\'ll be in your debt for a long time.' WHERE entry=8282;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent! With Deathclasp gone we\'re free to use the southern mountain range as a strategic path to circumvent the silithid hives. Your work is greatly appreciated.' WHERE entry=8283;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Just as I suspected.  I can decipher individual words in the tablets but they appear to be devoid of any logic or meaning.  It\'s not unknown for Twilight\'s Hammer sects to use a code to hide the meaning of their texts; we\'ll have to go to someone who knows more about this sort of thing.' WHERE entry=8284;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I see you\'re familiar with my old organization.  You must be with Cenarion Hold.  $B$BYou seek information to use against them?  Come closer, perhaps we can be of mutual assistance.' WHERE entry=8285;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='It is as it should be - the great one has risen. My watch comes to an end...' WHERE entry=8286;
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Has Anachronos returned?' WHERE entry=8286;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This is very interesting information indeed, $N.  This sheds some light on the presence of the Twilight\'s Hammer in Silithus and will undoubtedly help us in our struggle against them.  Your efforts will be handsomely rewarded, $C.' WHERE entry=8287;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Could you be the first to earn favor among the Bronze Flight IN a thousand years?' WHERE entry=8288;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='You have proven your value to our efforts in Warsong Gulch. Continue to aid the cause and bring me more talismans of merit. Do this, and you will earn even more of our trust.',objectives_loc2='You obtained a Silverwing Talisman of Merit for your last task, talk to me again, and you gain your reward.',offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you, $N. Your exploits in Warsong Gulch ring throughout Ashenvale Forest.' WHERE entry=8292;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='You have proven your value to our efforts in Warsong Gulch. Continue to rage against the Silverwing Sentinels! Bring me more marks of honor!',objectives_loc2='You obtained a Warsong Mark of Honor for your last task, talk to me again, and you gain your reward.',offerrewardtext_loc2='The night elves and their allies must tremble at even the whisper of your name! For the Horde!' WHERE entry=8293;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Captain Shatterskull roars in triumph.>$B$BHow much more can they withstand? How many more Alliance filth must perish at the hands of the Horde for them to retreat? Only time will tell, $R.' WHERE entry=8294;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You got the resources! Great job! I\'ll send the resources to our quartermasters, who can quickly disperse them to our troops.$B$BThank you, $N. Indeed, performing successful missions like the one you achieved are how wars are truly won.' WHERE entry=8297;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Very good. I will get these to our quartermasters immediately, and a commendation for your actions will be sent to my superiors.$B$BOnce again, thank you $N. Your contributions to our struggles are noticed by footman and field marshal alike.' WHERE entry=8298;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Very good. I will get these to our quartermasters immediately, and a commendation for your actions will be sent to my superiors.$B$BOnce again, thank you $N. Your contributions to our struggles are noticed by grunt and high warlord alike.' WHERE entry=8300;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You are not alone, hero. I will now grant you the ability to deputize others to help you IN your quest. If you are to be the champion of your people, you will need assistance IN your tasks and duties.' WHERE entry=8301;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, hero. You will now be granted the ability to deputize another Agent of Nozdormu.' WHERE entry=8302;
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc2='Anachronos',offerrewardtext_loc2='You are the hope of Kalimdor, $N.' WHERE entry=8303;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Commander Mar\'alith lowers his head in contemplation.>$B$BWhether she is alive or dead, I must do what is right. She must be found. Alas, I am bound by duty to this outpost. Will you help me once more, $N?' WHERE entry=8304;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You can feel a great sorrow revolving around this crystal. The force is so powerful that you feel as if you might collapse and die of sadness.' WHERE entry=8305;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Commander Mar\'alith clutches at his chest.>$B$BC\'Thun? WHAT is the meaning of all this? What is C\'Thun? How could this fiend have turned my sweet Natalia into the monster that you described?' WHERE entry=8306;
UPDATE locales_quest SET ObjectiveText1_loc2='The Fate of Mistress Natalia Mar\'alith' WHERE entry=8306;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This book contains several common recipes and a few unusual ones. After browsing through it for a few seconds you spot a recipe that involves sandworm meat.' WHERE entry=8307;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well this explains a lot. If you ever find a way into Ahn\'Qiraj, keep an eye out for ol\' Brann. I\'m afraid that he\'ll be powerless without his monkey.' WHERE entry=8308;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I can\'t make heads or tails of these glyphs. I\'ve never seen anything like it! I hope Frankal\'s research can shed some light on this mess.' WHERE entry=8309;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Outstanding! Don\'t wander off too far, kid. We might need you to take on another task or two.' WHERE entry=8310;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Wow, you got them all!  You\'re awesome!$B$BThank you for trick-or-treating for me.  Here, take these pumpkin treats - I think you\'ll like them a lot!$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End, $N!' WHERE entry=8311;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Wow, you got them all!  You\'re awesome!$B$BThank you for trick-or-treating for me.  Here, take these pumpkin treats - I think you\'ll like them a lot!$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End, $N!' WHERE entry=8312;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Let\'s have a look at that...$B$BThis seems simple enough.  They have their own names for some of the herbs, but those are simple enough to figure out.  Here, let me show you!' WHERE entry=8313;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The reason the dwarves could not decipher the glyphs is because there is nothing to decipher. The shifting outer layer of the prism must properly align with the inner crystal\'s markings in order for the message to be transmitted. Clever...$B$BWhile we should be able to translate this data, we must first unlock the code. There is only one clue on the surface of the prism - assuming the rubbings were transferred correctly - and it looks grim.' WHERE entry=8314;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I hold 20,000 years of history in my hands, $N!' WHERE entry=8315;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='War comes, $N, and with it comes untold horrors. You have done all that could be asked of you and for that you should be rewarded.$B$BShould this... this prophecy ever come to pass...$B$B<Geologist Larksbane turns pale.>$B$BThe future of us all could be at an end.$B$BThese armaments will prove invaluable to your campaign in this desert.' WHERE entry=8316;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent! You\'re a life saver. These dumplings turned out to be quite good. Didn\'t really expect such good taste from the Twilight\'s Hammer.' WHERE entry=8317;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent!  I\'ll stash these away, maybe they\'ll be useful later.' WHERE entry=8318;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent work!  I\'ll put a good word in for you.' WHERE entry=8319;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='That was a task well performed, $N.  Your slaying of the Twilight geolords must have dealt a grievous blow to the cult.  Let us hope their plans are slowed...' WHERE entry=8320;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve done it!  Vyral is killed!  This can only mean doom for the Twilight Hammer\'s operations in Silithus. There may be more of them scurrying about, but the blow you dealt to the cult today is one from which they will not easily recover.' WHERE entry=8321;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The keg is filled with ale.$B$BHaving successfully fought your way inside the inn, you now place the eggs inside the keg. You can smell the foul odor permeating the air...' WHERE entry=8322;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent!  I will get to decoding these as soon as possible.  If I find anything of interest I\'ll find some way to get the information to you.' WHERE entry=8323;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent!  I can\'t wait to read these. Please do keep bringing the encrypted texts here if you find them.' WHERE entry=8324;
UPDATE locales_quest SET objectives_loc2='Kill 8 Mana Wyrms; they are located close to the Burning Crystals that are adjacent to the tower and gazebo.  Return to Magistrix Erona at the tower on Sunstrider Isle when you are done.',offerrewardtext_loc2='For your toubles you may choose your reward.' WHERE entry=8325;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The tower and surrounding areas should now be relatively secure, though only for the time being.  You have done well in providing us with a buffer of security, but we will need to reassert control over the entire isle if we are to survive here in the long run.  This will involve tackling much greater threats than errant mana wyrms and lynxes.$B$BTake this, $N - you will no doubt make good use of it for the tasks to come.' WHERE entry=8326;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Magistrix Erona told me you\'d be along quick enough, $N. The Falthrien Academy to our west - the huge floating building with the ornate spires - is in bad shape. You\'re going to be leading the effort to recapture it from one of the Wretched - a $R who has forever succumbed to their basest cravings.$B$BI hope you\'re ready to work. This is not only going to be a lesson about danger, but also of what happens when you forsake the realities of who you are.' WHERE entry=8327;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, $N - I believe you\'re one of the new mages here on the isle, yes? Well, you\'ve come to the right place. If arcane mastery is what you seek, then I can provide such knowledge - as long as you have the wherewithal to handle training costs and the capacity to focus on the lessons I\'ll be teaching.$B$BLet\'s get started!' WHERE entry=8328;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done - I knew you\'d be perfect for the task.  Once it\'s safe to make use of our outdoor facilities on the isle, I\'ll be putting these things to good use.$B$BLike I mentioned, please feel free to keep the satchel.  Also, you may find this piece of armor to be useful.  Consider it ample compensation for a simple task performed dutifully!' WHERE entry=8330;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='$N, good day. I was told you will pit yourself against the Abyssal Council? If that is so, then listen closely to my next words...' WHERE entry=8331;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, very good. I\'ve been working on the medallion - now with these last ingredients, I\'ll be done in just a few moments...$B$BThere we are. Here is the medallion, $N.$B$BYou\'ll need to wear this when you activate one of the Twilight\'s Hammer\'s wind stones. Put this on, along with the rest of the twilight trappings, and the Abyssal Council will see you as one of their cultist underlings.' WHERE entry=8332;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Here you are, $N. One more Twilight medallion of station. Use it well, and I wish you luck against the Abyssal Council!' WHERE entry=8333;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='While the deaths of the tenders give me no joy whatsoever, it does show me that you\'re ready for the most important task you\'ll do here on Sunstrider Isle. Take this and put it to good use; you\'ll need good items and sharp wits for the task ahead. Our reassertion of control over the island depends on it.' WHERE entry=8334;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Felendren\'s head... you are to be commended, $N.  You\'ve succeeded where others, like Felendren, have utterly failed.  Perhaps you are truly ready to be a contributing member of $R society.$B$BYour success here means that you are capable of surviving the greater threats that lurk in Eversong... and believe me, there are plenty to face.' WHERE entry=8335;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Splendid - these will do nicely.  I\'ve been doing quite a bit of thinking on the current malaise Sunstrider Isle suffers under.  One possible course of action I had pondered was to collect these arcane slivers from the beasts on the isle.  In doing so, they could be experimented on; this would provide a potential source of culpability.$B$BAnyway, I will tend to the research.  Allow me to place this incantation on you.  I believe you\'ll make good use of it!' WHERE entry=8336;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This is... most interesting.  And when I say interesting, I mean more disturbing than anything else.$B$BOur efforts to reassert control over the isle in the time following the destruction of the Sunwell have been a challenge.  I suspect that whatever foul source is corrupting the isle is at the heart of it all; this sliver may be of some aid in uncovering what\'s really going on.$B$BYou were wise to bring this to me, $N. Take this as compensation for your diligence.  Thank you.' WHERE entry=8338;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thanks. Just one moment and I\'ll have that ring ready for you...$B$BThere it is. Now you\'re ready.$B$BBe sure to wear this ring, along with a medallion of station and the rest of the twilight trappings, when you activate a greater wind stone. Do that, and the Abyssal Council will think you one of their servants. Then, perhaps you can lure one into an ambush!' WHERE entry=8341;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, I see your convictions are strong. Not many will face that council of fiends!$B$BHere\'s your ring, $N. May your will, and your fortune, stand firm.' WHERE entry=8342;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='What Huum says is true. I believe I know how to summon a lord of the Abyssal Council! Listen on, and I will explain...' WHERE entry=8343;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done!  Yes, this should be enough essence to get started on my research.  I have a strong feeling that this tainted essence will be just the thing... the window, as I mentioned.$B$BFollowing the orders of your masters is highly recommended as a young $C.  As I promised you, here is the reward for obeying instructions and completing them in a competent manner - the knowledge to summon and bind your own imp.$B$BUse it well, $N' WHERE entry=8344;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, $N - thank you for sharing your experience at the Shrine of Dath\'Remar. First off, you should be commended for your sense of duty and respect - it will serve you well not only here, but in all of Azeroth as well.$B$BAs for the odd sensation, it is no doubt a contributing part of the taint that has befallen Sunstrider Isle. We shall keep an eye on it; thank you for alerting us to it!' WHERE entry=8345;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='If there is only one lesson you deign to remember from your time on Sunstrider Isle, let it be this - control your thirst for magic.  It is a thirst unending, $N - you must absorb energy to survive via Mana Tap, and you must control how you release it via Arcane Torrent.  Failure is to become one of the Wretched... hopelessly addicted and insane.$B$BSeek out creatures on the isle that have mana and Mana Tap them.  Learn to master your cravings of power.  When you have sufficiently fed, return to me.',objectives_loc2='Use your Mana Tap racial ability on creatures with mana six times, then return to Arcanist Helion.',offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve done well today, $N. Your willingness to learn shows that you may very well rise above the unyielding cravings you must endure as a $R.$B$BRest not on your laurels, young one, but instead seek to master what you have learned. Only through diligence will we as a race survive.$B$BTake this' WHERE entry=8346;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well hello there, $C! I heard that a resourceful young $R formerly in the service of Magistrix Erona might be making their way down here to help us Outrunners out. We certainly welcome the help, especially from someone who\'s proven to be so competent.$B$BI hope you\'re interested in running an errand or two for us.' WHERE entry=8347;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I knew you were a tough $C the minute I saw you walk into Cenarion Hold. Keep it up!' WHERE entry=8348;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Good to see you again, $C! So you had a medallion made? Good -- you\'ll need that for your next quest...' WHERE entry=8349;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you, I do appreciate the prompt delivery.$B$BWhile you\'re here, please make yourself comfortable.  If you haven\'t done so already, feel free to get a hearthstone and bind yourself here.  Using a hearthstone will allow you to recall to an inn once every hour.  If you ever lose your hearthstone, simply return to any inn - an innkeeper will gladly get you a new one.' WHERE entry=8350;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yes, that\'s right, $N. I have a very tough task ahead...' WHERE entry=8351;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You... you did it! You did it, $N! Here! Take this. It\'s the biggest chest we had lying around and I filled it with some of the best stuff we found.' WHERE entry=8352;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Too funny!  Well done, $N! Here\'s your treat.$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End!' WHERE entry=8353;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Too funny!  Well done, $N! Here\'s your treat.$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End!' WHERE entry=8354;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Too funny!  Well done, $N! Here\'s your treat.$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End!' WHERE entry=8355;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You are truly mighty, haha! Well done, and thanks for being such a good sport. Here\'s your candy.$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End, $N!' WHERE entry=8356;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'re quite the dancing machine, $N!$B$BHere\'s your treat for being such a good sport. Happy Hallow\'s End, and give my best to your sick little friend! I hope they get better soon.' WHERE entry=8357;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Woo-woo! Well done, $N! Here\'s your treat.$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End!' WHERE entry=8358;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You are truly mighty, haha! Well done, and thanks for being such a good sport. Here\'s your candy.$B$BHappy Hallow\'s End, $N!' WHERE entry=8359;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'re quite the dancing machine, $N!$B$BHere\'s your treat for being such a good sport. Happy Hallow\'s End, and give my best to your sick little friend! I hope they get better soon.' WHERE entry=8360;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Hah! You did it, $N! The Twilight\'s Hammer will soon be crushed!' WHERE entry=8361;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve done well! That\'s less Templars for me to worry about.$B$BHere you go, $N. Hope there\'s something useful in there for you.' WHERE entry=8362;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent, $N!  Defeating those Dukes will leave the Twilight\'s Hammer reeling for a while. As promised, here\'s your reward. It\'s some of the better stuff Huum and I have found.' WHERE entry=8363;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I knew you\'d come through, $N! Here\'s your reward.' WHERE entry=8364;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Oh you\'re a darling, even if it did take you longer than I am accustomed to. This shipment should make me quite a bit of money once I\'ve cleaned and personalized these hats. And seeing as I\'m always willing to reward work that\'s well done, here\'s a little something for you. I suggest that you spend some of it on a bath sweetie.' WHERE entry=8365;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='$N! You are the man!!!$B$BI\'m sure that the Cartel will ease up on me now that you\'ve dealt with those Southsea scum. Let\'s see, what can I give you as a reward? How about a little coin and you choose from one of these for your trouble?' WHERE entry=8366;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Your trials have not been easy, but your courage did not escape you and your strength did not fail. Part with past tokens of victory, $C. None shall need them as a reminder of your worth. Stand up straight, $N. Today you will walk with great pride for you are a hero!' WHERE entry=8367;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent! You\'ve shown your worth by defending our operations in Warsong Gulch! May word of your honor spread far and wide across our lands.' WHERE entry=8368;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve shown great bravery in protecting our lands in Alterac Valley! I will tell my superiors of your deeds.' WHERE entry=8369;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Securing our resources in Arathi is an important task! You\'ve done well, $N.' WHERE entry=8370;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'re not one to disappoint, $N! What you\'ve learned goes beyond petty medals and commendations. What you\'ve learned is what can only come with experience and the hardening of one\'s temper in the field of battle.$B$BYou\'ve done well, $C. You\'re a true hero of the Alliance!' WHERE entry=8371;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, $N! You\'ve served the Alliance well.' WHERE entry=8372;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ah, it almost smells better around here already. Almost.$B$BThanks to you, $N, Southshore just might make it through another Hallow\'s End. Here\'s your treats, with my thanks! If you run out of candy, I think there\'s a gnome named Katrina Shimmerstar in Ironforge who can sell you more; she\'s only around during Hallow\'s End, I believe.' WHERE entry=8373;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Good work, soldier! Keep it up and we\'ll have the Horde running all the way back to Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=8374;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve shown great bravery in protecting our lands in Alterac Valley! I will tell my superiors of your deeds.' WHERE entry=8375;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='War comes, $N, and with it comes untold horrors. You have done all that could be asked of you and for that you should be rewarded.$B$BShould this... this prophecy ever come to pass...$B$B<Geologist Larksbane turns pale.>$B$BThe future of us all could be at an end.$B$BThese armaments will prove invaluable to your campaign in this desert.' WHERE entry=8376;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='War comes, $N, and with it comes untold horrors. You have done all that could be asked of you and for that you should be rewarded.$B$BShould this... this prophecy ever come to pass...$B$B<Geologist Larksbane turns pale.>$B$BThe future of us all could be at an end.$B$BThese armaments will prove invaluable to your campaign in this desert.' WHERE entry=8377;
