UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='A deal is a deal. I sure hope you know what you are getting yourself into, $N. This is an awful lot of trouble to go through to do some fishing.' WHERE entry=8728;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, $N. I will be able to reform the Scepter of the Shifting Sands soon.' WHERE entry=8729;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Vaelastrasz\'s soul is at ease, champion. The Aspects all watch your progress with great interest. Know that you have powerful allies.$B$BI was commanded to grant you something to aid you in this struggle. Use it well...' WHERE entry=8730;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I can tell that Krug has little use for paperwork. He signed this in silithid blood!$B$BVery well, $N. I\'ve prepared a set of tasks that should make good use of your skills as a $C.$B$BWith the continued efforts of you and people like you, our enemy will soon be crushed!' WHERE entry=8731;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yes, I suppose that little skirmish will pass as field duty nowadays. Take these back to Cenarion Hold, I\'m sure they\'ll have a cushy job ready for you.$B$BOff you go!' WHERE entry=8732;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The wisp is silent except for a low humming sound. Oddly enough, it is able to communicate with you through thoughts.' WHERE entry=8733;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='It would be impossible to pull Eranikus from the Dream should he refuse. His intentions, however, require him to enter our world. He seeks to destroy the living manifestation of Malfurion. To do this successfully would mean an end to one of the most powerful allies of the Dream. The Nightmare would wholly consume all that would remain should Malfurion fall...' WHERE entry=8734;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Are you prepared? Is the world prepared for what we are about to invoke? I do not know... I am bound by duty to Malfurion. Duty and honor...' WHERE entry=8735;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='He is redeemed, $N. He now returns to the Dream to right what he alone has done wrong. Eranikus will be a powerful ally to Malfurion and my father.$B$BThese armaments are for you, $N; given to me by Ysera herself. You would do well to make use of them in your battles against the Qiraji.' WHERE entry=8736;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Good job, $N.  Here\'s your next assignment.' WHERE entry=8737;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Your efforts are greatly appreciated, $N. I\'ll read these scouting reports right away, feel free to go over your next assignment.' WHERE entry=8738;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Your efforts are greatly appreciated, $N. I\'ll read these scouting reports right away, feel free to go over your next assignment.' WHERE entry=8739;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, $N. The twilight marauders were inflicting an unacceptable number of casualties on our patrols. Here\'s your next assignment.' WHERE entry=8740;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Your deeds will be known to all, champion. They will sing your praises from Orgrimmar to the far reaches of the South Seas. All will know of the champion of the Bronze Flight, $N.' WHERE entry=8741;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='A thousand years has passed and just as it was fated, one stands before me. One who shall lead their people to a new age.$BThe Old God trembles, $N. Oh yes, it fears your faith. Shatter the prophecy of C\'Thun.$BIt knows you come, champion - and with you comes the might of Kalimdor. You have only to let me know when you are prepared and I shall grant you The Scepter of the Shifting Sands.',offerrewardtext_loc2='The Scepter of the Shifting Sands is whole once more, $N.$BIt must be you who uses the scepter. It must be you who heralds the next age of your people. You must wait for the armies of the Horde and the Alliance to arrive in Silithus before you may ring the Scarab Gong.' WHERE entry=8742;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='From the ground near the gong springs a special crystal. Perhaps favor from the Brood.' WHERE entry=8743;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The tag on this present reads:$B$BTo $N,$B$BMay your feast of Great-Winter be merry and bright!' WHERE entry=8744;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You did it!  Huzzah!$B$BMetzen flew back into Great-father Winter\'s stables - yes Metzen can really fly - just a little while ago!  The dust worked like a charm; I knew it would.  You\'ve saved the Feast of Winter Veil as well as Smokywood Pastures from disaster.  Thank you, $N.$B$BListen... because of what you\'ve done here, I want you to have this.  It\'s something VERY special; if you have a mount, I think you\'ll get a kick out of it.  Happy Winter Veil!' WHERE entry=8746;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Impressive, little one. You have gone through much trouble to gain the favor of the Bronze Flight. Your dedication is noted.$B$BThe signet ring of the protector will offer superior protection against the forces of evil.$B$BBe warned, once you have chosen your path, you will have no recourse should you change your mind.' WHERE entry=8747;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Your rise amongst the rank of the Brood is most impressive, $N. May you never stray from the path of the protector!' WHERE entry=8748;
