UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank you for rescuing me... I feared for my life. Please accept this as a small token of my gratitude.$B$BAnthion is... no... he can\'t be...' WHERE entry=8945;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='That locket... you found her! I can rest in peace at long last.$B$BI shall now answer any questions you might have, $N. But make haste, my time in this world is not long.' WHERE entry=8946;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent. I shall transmute these into something more suitable to our needs.' WHERE entry=8947;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Anthion sent you, you say? I thought he was dead. I guess I\'ve heard stranger things in my life.$B$BVery well, then.  What is it you want me to do with this banner?' WHERE entry=8948;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Hmmm... strangely enough I don\'t feel any better about my brother\'s death at the hands of those brutes.$B$BWell, you held your end of the bargain. Let\'s see what I can do for you.' WHERE entry=8949;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yes, these will do just fine. After I\'m done, no force in the world will be able to stop your victim from accepting your challenge.' WHERE entry=8950;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I can\'t believe our lives are all but forfeit all because of a stupid medallion! And you\'re sure Anthion mentioned Bodley?$B$BWell, you\'ve done your job so let\'s get your reward out of the way.' WHERE entry=8951;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I can\'t believe our lives are all but forfeit all because of a stupid medallion! And you\'re sure Anthion mentioned Bodley?$B$BWell, you\'ve done your job so let\'s get your reward out of the way.' WHERE entry=8952;
