UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc2='Corastrasza',offerrewardtext_loc2='It\'s quite presumptuous of you to interfere in the personal affairs of a dragon, don\'t you think, $R?$B$BThat aside, it would be wrong of me not to let my brother know that I am well. You may tell your meddling friend that I will keep my brother abreast of my actions.' WHERE entry=13412;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='My drake tells me that with practice, you might become a capable combatant.$B$BVery well, then. In the interest of our war on Malygos, I shall allow you to practice with my pets at your leisure.$B$BMake ready, $R, for he is a fierce and unforgiving opponent.' WHERE entry=13413;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I noticed some improvement today, $C. At moments, it was as if you were one with the drake.$B$BYou are welcome to practice with my precious pets at your leisure.' WHERE entry=13414;
