UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Your trials have not been easy, but your courage did not escape you and your strength did not fail. Part with past tokens of victory, $C. None shall need them as a reminder of your worth. Stand up straight, $N. Today you will walk with great pride for you are a hero!' WHERE entry=13476;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You live up to yer reputation, $N. Without people like you, the Alliance wouldn\'t stand a chance against the savage forces of the Horde.' WHERE entry=13477;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'re not one to disappoint, $N! What you\'ve learned goes beyond petty medals and commendations. What you\'ve learned is what can only come with experience and the hardening of one\'s temper in the field of battle.$B$BYou\'ve done well, $C. You\'re a true hero of the Alliance!' WHERE entry=13478;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent, excellent, thank you! I may need more of a sample to get truly conclusive results, but you\'ve done well today.' WHERE entry=13479;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent, excellent, thank you! I may need more of a sample to get truly conclusive results, but you\'ve done well today.' WHERE entry=13480;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You have done well. We thought Father Kamaros lost, for certain. Your bravery will serve as an example to all those who oppose the Scourge.' WHERE entry=13481;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Thank the Light. I\'d thought Father Kamaros dead, or worse. Through your bravery and compassion, you have restored a great ally to the Argent Crusade. You have my thanks and those of the crusade.' WHERE entry=13482;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yes! Yes, I think I have just the task for you...' WHERE entry=13483;
