UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Very fine specimens indeed, $N! These are sure to provide many hours of curious speculation amongst my colleagues back home.' WHERE entry=13549;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='One, two, three,... hehe, that be a good number o\' them, mon! Now we be safe for quite some time!' WHERE entry=13556;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The Sons of Hodir accept your tribute, small one. You continue to prove your worth as an ally in more ways than one.' WHERE entry=13559;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Above the stale, unwashed stench, you catch a whiff of a familiar smell!  It appears as if this once-mighty adventurer has a real love for kungaloosh.$B$BPeeking through the bars, you can barely make out the recipe written on his arm....' WHERE entry=13571;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Welcome back from your exercises, $N. Even while we practice for the competition, it\'s good to remind ourselves that the Scourge is still out there.' WHERE entry=13592;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='We are proud that you have agreed to train with us and compete on our behalf.' WHERE entry=13593;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<The marshal accepts the Blade of Drak\'Mar from you.>$B$BA fine weapon, and perfectly balanced. It will serve me well in the next match.' WHERE entry=13600;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='So the tales were true? This is a fine blade and I have no doubt that it will serve me well in the tournament. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE entry=13603;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The platinum disc fits perfectly inside the console. It begins to spin as its contents are scanned by white beams of light.' WHERE entry=13604;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent job, $N. We\'re one step closer to saving Azeroth!' WHERE entry=13606;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='It\'s locked? Figures!$B$BLet\'s see what information this junk heap can give us...' WHERE entry=13607;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ye did it! I don\'t know how, but ye did!' WHERE entry=13609;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Ye never cease to impress, $N.$B$BYe and me are having a pint together after all this is done, ye hear me?' WHERE entry=13610;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I\'ve got to hand it to you, $N. Our odds might not be the best, but I feel a lot better with you lending a hand.' WHERE entry=13611;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Stand by for verification.$B$BAccess to the Celestial Planetarium granted. Please retrieve your key.' WHERE entry=13614;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The blade is as fine as the stories say. It would seem there\'s little reason to complete the repairs on my customary blade. Winter\'s Edge is far superior and I will continue to carry it. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE entry=13616;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, $N. Mounted combat is often hard to pick up for those accustomed to fighting on foot. I have no doubt that you\'ll continue to improve with practice, which is more than I can say for some warriors.' WHERE entry=13625;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='All excellent planks, and the price is right, too! Even better, those Argent Crusade sticks-in-the-mud will never know. They\'ll get their precious coliseum and I\'ll get my early completion bonus. Now that\'s a win-win if I ever saw one.' WHERE entry=13627;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Object integrity confirmed.  Please hold while solidified residue is removed.' WHERE entry=13629;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'re here.  Let us hope this works.  For all our sakes.' WHERE entry=13631;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='So you\'re saying this knight\'s story is a sham? Most suspicious. Dishonorable at the least, and murderous at the worst. Still, we can\'t confront him until we know for certain whether he was involved in these murders.$B$BDo nothing to arouse his suspicions, $N. Discretion will serve us well as we continue to investigate.' WHERE entry=13633;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='So you\'re saying this knight\'s story is a sham? Most suspicious. Dishonorable at the least, and murderous at the worst. Still, we can\'t confront him until we know for certain whether he was involved in these murders.$B$BDo nothing to arouse his suspicions, $N. Discretion will serve us well as we continue to investigate.' WHERE entry=13634;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This one will do nicely. All that remains is to imbue it with the power of the Light, giving it the ability to find truth amid deception.' WHERE entry=13641;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='So you say Lorien Sunblaze was done in by poison and Sir Wendell was burnt alive? Dreadful ways to die, both of them. Only Conall was killed by cold steel, and from your description, it was a coward\'s strike, not honorable combat that laid him in his grave.$B$BAll three sparred with and were scheduled to fight the Black Knight. This cannot be a coincidence. Now, we must find a way to prove it was the Black Knight\'s work.' WHERE entry=13643;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Crusader Rhydalla examines the bag\'s contents with a look of disgust on her face.>$B$BIt\'s all here, $N: the poison that killed Lorien, a collection of knives, torches, and oil. No man has cause to possess these things here and no squire would do so without orders from his knightly master. We\'ve found our murderer, $N, but who is he working for?' WHERE entry=13654;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Keep the residue pouring in!' WHERE entry=13662;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Crusader Rhydalla\'s face pales as she reads the orders.>$B$BThis can only mean one thing, $N. The Black Knight is a member of the Cult of the Damned and has been sent by Arthas to disrupt the tournament!$B$BThe Black Knight has proven himself a fearsome combatant, and you will need to be every bit as good if you wish to face him. When you are a champion, return to me and we\'ll find a way to ensure his defeat.' WHERE entry=13663;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='With the death of the Black Knight, the tournament may once again serve its purpose. The champions of the Horde and Alliance may demonstrate their skill at arms and train for the day when Arthas and his minions will no longer threaten us.$B$BYou have the thanks of the Argent Crusade, $N, and that of all who have answered our call.' WHERE entry=13664;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done. Training against the other valiants is one of the best ways to prepare yourself for tournament competition. I know you\'ll make Stormwind proud, $N.' WHERE entry=13665;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='So there is some truth to those old tales? It seems they did not lie about the quality of the blade. Well done, $N. The champion who wields it will be a lucky man, indeed.' WHERE entry=13666;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I have entered your name in the rolls, $N. As an aspirant you will train with others who wish to compete in the tournament and hone your mounted combat skills. Once you have proven yourself, you will be allowed to enter the lowest rank of competition on behalf of your capital city.' WHERE entry=13667;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I have entered your name in the rolls, $N. As an aspirant you will train with others who wish to compete in the tournament and hone your mounted combat skills. Once you have proven yourself, you will be allowed to enter the lowest rank of competition on behalf of your capital city.' WHERE entry=13668;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='There\'s no doubt that this is a blade of exquisite quality and balance. Now I understand why these weapons are so coveted among the champions of the Alliance.' WHERE entry=13669;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The blade is as fine as the squire said it would be, but where did he find out about it? No matter; it will serve its new owner well. Perhaps it\'s only fair that Ironforge\'s grand champion be the one to wield it.' WHERE entry=13670;
