UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc2='Most of the tournament\'s competitions require competitors to master the command of a mount in battle. In order to familiarize you with mounted combat, we\'ve put up training dummies all over the northern part of the tournament grounds.$B$BVisit the stables outside the pavilion, equip your lance, and mount up on the Sunreaver hawkstrider. Familiarize yourself with the mount and use its abilities to defeat the three different kinds of training dummies. $B',offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, $N. Mounted combat is often hard to pick up for those accustomed to fighting on foot. I have no doubt that you\'ll continue to improve with practice, which is more than I can say for some warriors.' WHERE entry=13677;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Very well, I will make the arrangements.' WHERE entry=13678;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Congratulations are in order, $N. You have bested your challenger and earned the right to advance to the rank of valiant.' WHERE entry=13679;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Congratulations are in order, $N. You have bested your challenger and earned the right to advance to the rank of valiant.' WHERE entry=13680;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='These should do. Just don\'t go around blabbing to those crusaders about where you got them from. I\'m sure they\'ll get upset. But, hey, it\'s not like the titans have come back for them. They\'re fair game, I say. Good work, $N.' WHERE entry=13681;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='$N, you and your allies have spared the tournament from a devastating attack. Though our skytalon riders are brave, they have their hands full keeping the peace on the tournament grounds and would be hard-pressed to defend the skies against the cult\'s attack. You have the thanks of the Argent Crusade and all who have gathered here to compete.' WHERE entry=13682;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Welcome aboard then, Valiant $N. The Stormwind delegation is proud to count you among its members.' WHERE entry=13684;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='It\'s good to meet you, valiant. Ironforge needs competitors like you to prevail in the tournament.' WHERE entry=13685;
