UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='$N, you have spared the tournament from a devastating attack. The Argent Crusade and all who gather here are in our debt and we\'ll make certain they remember it. For all their bluster about providing protection, the peacekeepers and skytalons spend more time breaking up drunken brawls than keeping us safe from the Scourge.$B$BIt\'s no matter. We always protect our own.' WHERE entry=13788;
