UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE entry=24221;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent news, $C! If our tactical deployments continue to be this successful, the Horde will be in full retreat before long.' WHERE entry=24223;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE entry=24224;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE entry=24225;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE entry=24226;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='There is no greater honor than driving invaders from Horde territories. We salute your great courage in aiding our forces today!' WHERE entry=24426;
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='You\'re back!  Do you bring news of victory?' WHERE entry=24426;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Just what I wanted to hear!  A victory in Alterac Valley - even a temporary one - is crucial to our overall strategy against the Horde.' WHERE entry=24427;
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc2='Tell me, $N. What news do you bring from the front?' WHERE entry=24427;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='What? How did you get this? Isn\'t she... Never mind the details, I suppose. You\'ll be wanting one of these baubles as recompense, no doubt.' WHERE entry=24428;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve brought me the head of someone who is... No, best not to think about it too hard. You\'ll be wanting recompense for your heroic deeds, no doubt.' WHERE entry=24429;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This is quite a find, $N. I can\'t have you selling this to anyone else, so I\'m willing to offer generously.' WHERE entry=24431;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Mariel accepts the orders and the captured seeing crystal and examines both.>$B$BGood work, $N, and quick thinking. I\'m sure the theft of this trinket won\'t slow them down for long, but I think you\'ve bought us time to warn the leaders of the Horde and Alliance about the impending attacks.' WHERE entry=24442;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent work. Now that this is in our hands, we must get it to Myralion Sunblaze as soon as possible. We can\'t risk the Silver Covenant taking the book from us again.$B$BI\'ll get that tabard back to Shandy and see that he\'s well compensated for his assistance. Once the book is in Myralion\'s hands, the Silver Covenant won\'t be a threat anymore.' WHERE entry=24451;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Caladis accepts the heavy book and begins leafing through it.>$B$BI knew the symbols on the blade were familiar. The weapon was most certainly forged by the dragons and gifted to one of the mortal races, but which blade is this, and how did it come to rest in Icecrown?' WHERE entry=24454;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar, although Blood-Queen Lana\'thel proclaimed we could not! The blade must still be tempered, but she and her master will not stand in our way!' WHERE entry=24461;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I... I don\'t understand. Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade to its original condition. What has happened here?' WHERE entry=24476;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I had not thought it possible for evil to take hold in such a sword, but I suppose it was naive of me. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BUther\'s advice is wise, $N, and I would urge you to heed it quickly.' WHERE entry=24480;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE entry=24498;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Just in time! Thank you, $N.$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... or maybe, just maybe, his redemption.' WHERE entry=24499;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Jaina is still catching her breath.>$B$BI can barely believe we\'re still alive. It was foolish of me to follow him. I\'ve made that mistake too many times.  And you... it was reckless of you to come after me instead of escaping with the information! But... well... thank you. You truly are a hero.$B$BWith Uther\'s guidance, we may stand a chance at defeating Arthas. All the lives lost today were not in vain.' WHERE entry=24500;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Good. $N, I know of you. You\'ll be perfect for these tasks.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE entry=24506;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE entry=24507;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='$N! I\'m so glad you\'ve come.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE entry=24510;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well timed, $C!$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... and a route to vengeance long overdue.' WHERE entry=24511;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Admit you to the Sunwell? That\'s impossible! The Sunwell is the most sacred and important site of our people. We have only recently reclaimed it with the help of the Shattered Sun Offensive. It is not a place for tourists or travelers.' WHERE entry=24522;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I confess that I did not expect Thalorien\'s spirit to recognize you as the heir to Quel\'Delar, but I defer to his judgment. You may enter the Sunwell, but I remind you that you are a guest in the most our most sacred of precincts, and you should act accordingly.' WHERE entry=24535;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='A deep sense of dread washes over you as the flame devours the items.' WHERE entry=24545;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This is unbelievable, $N. You\'ve really done it! All of the quel\'dorei have heard of Thalorien Dawnseeker and Quel\'Delar, but no one ever thought the sword would be restored.' WHERE entry=24553;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Myralion takes the hilt from you and scrutinizes the artifact.>$B$BThis came from the citadel? What was it doing there? This blade is certainly not of Scourge manufacture.$B$BWeapons of this quality can only be crafted by a few of Azeroth\'s creatures. We will have to consult them and see if they can help us identify it.' WHERE entry=24554;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='We must recover that book from the Silver Covenant. Without that book from Krasus, we stand little chance of solving the mystery of the sword in Icecrown or unlocking its power.' WHERE entry=24555;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I knew Shandy would find a way to make it work. Let me get this enchanted and ready for you to use. With any luck, the tabard\'s owner won\'t even know it\'s missing and Shandy will cover the rest of our tracks.' WHERE entry=24556;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Magister Hathorel reads the captured orders.>$B$BThe agent you intercepted was supposed to deliver the Wyrmrest tome to Icecrown, after meeting with one Arcanist Tybalin inside the Silver Enclave. We have to reclaim that book, $N, and we only have one chance before it leaves the city. We have to work quickly.' WHERE entry=24557;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='<Myralion accepts the heavy book and begins leafing through it.>$B$BThose symbols on the blade seemed familiar and now there\'s little wonder why. This is certainly a dragon blade, gifted to one of the mortal races, but which blade is this, and how did it come to rest in Icecrown?' WHERE entry=24558;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar in defiance of that Blood-Queen Lana\'thel\'s pronouncement! Now, the blade must be tempered before we can show her the folly of her words.' WHERE entry=24559;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade. Why hasn\'t it worked?' WHERE entry=24560;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='How can evil take root in such a sword? I would not have thought it possible if the evidence wasn\'t here before my eyes. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BI believe Uther is right. You must heed his advice quickly, $N.' WHERE entry=24561;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I hope you understand that I can\'t just admit you to the Sunwell, $N. This is the most sacred place known to the sin\'dorei and we have only recently regained control over it.$B$BYou would raise the hopes of our people with tales of Quel\'Delar? Without proof of the truth of your claims, I see no reason to take you at your word.' WHERE entry=24562;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You truly do carry Quel\'Delar. This is a great day for all of Quel\'Thalas and the sin\'dorei. You have my leave to enter the Sunwell and finish the sword\'s restoration. Keep your head high, $N. The children of Silvermoon have dreamt of this day for years.' WHERE entry=24563;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE entry=24564;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='With Sartharion slain, surely Deathwing and Sinestra\'s plans are now stalled.' WHERE entry=24579;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Word of your success precedes you, $C. Anub\'Rekhan is no more. You did him a great service, $N.' WHERE entry=24580;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='That\'s one less thorn in our side. With Noth destroyed, Scourge research into refining the means of creating the undead will grind to a halt.' WHERE entry=24581;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well done, $C. The Scourge military command out of Naxxramas has been thrown into disarray by Razuvious\'s demise.' WHERE entry=24582;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Children everywhere will sleep easier knowing that Patchwerk is no more.' WHERE entry=24583;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='With Malygos defeated, the Nexus War should come to a swift conclusion. You have the gratitude of the Kirin Tor, $N.' WHERE entry=24584;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I never cease to be amazed by the horrors that can be created through the use of technology.' WHERE entry=24585;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Now Veranus can finally rest in peace.' WHERE entry=24586;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I trust that you did not have to face too many of his iron construct assistants?' WHERE entry=24587;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The greatest weakness of Ulduar is its masters\' blind faith in their inventions to protect it.' WHERE entry=24588;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='All of Azeroth is fortunate that Timear foresaw the Eredar lord\'s arrival and that you were there in time to slay him.' WHERE entry=24589;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The Frozen Throne is without its chief guardian thanks to you. Our attacks upon the Lich King\'s forces will be all the more successful now.' WHERE entry=24590;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE entry=24594;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This is unbelievable, $N. You\'ve really done it! All of the quel\'dorei have heard of Thalorien Dawnseeker and Quel\'Delar, but no one ever thought the sword would be restored.' WHERE entry=24595;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE entry=24598;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Lovely work, $N! People will be tripping over one another to get Crown chocolates now that they\'ve had a chance to taste those sweet, romantic treats.$B$BHere\'s a little something for helping us out.' WHERE entry=24636;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Hey, thanks, kid. Give it over, let\'s take a look.
<He takes the device from you and fiddles with it.>
Oh, that ain\'t good.' WHERE entry=24655;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You got it, huh? Good job, kid. Top notch. Let\'s see what we got here.
<He cracks open the crate and rummages around inside.>' WHERE entry=24656;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You got his ledger? Really? That\'s great, $N. There\'s probably loads of good information in here.' WHERE entry=24657;
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc2='REUSE ME' WHERE entry=24661;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE entry=24664;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE entry=24666;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Incapable fools. I begin to wonder if any of these louts from the tournament will be of any use at all. Perhaps you\'ll prove me wrong.' WHERE entry=24682;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I underestimated this Scourgelord, and it\'s my men that paid for it. When I think that my guilt over Arthas\' betrayal cannot go any deeper, he proves me wrong yet again.$B$BWe have to press on. We cannot let their sacrifice be meaningless.' WHERE entry=24683;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Such a senseless waste! Arthas goes too far! I can only hope what we find in the Halls of Reflection makes this somehow worth it.$B$BIf what that vile gnome said is to be trusted, Frostmourne should be there, and with it, answers to confronting Arthas.' WHERE entry=24710;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The Halls of Reflection. Finally.$B$BLet me know when you are ready. Arthas may not be here, but it would be naive to think that he would leave Frostmourne unguarded entirely.' WHERE entry=24711;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The Halls of Reflection lie ahead. If what that vile gnome said is to be trusted, Frostmourne should be there, and with it, answers to confronting Arthas.' WHERE entry=24712;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='The Halls of Reflection. Finally.$B$BLet me know when you are ready, $C. I will not be so naive as to think that Arthas left his precious sword entirely unguarded.' WHERE entry=24713;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Listen well, $C. In accepting this weapon your fate is sealed.$B$BOvercome or succumb.$B$BI have placed your feet upon this path. You are therefore my personal responsibility. Should you falter, I am duty-bound to deliver you from this life.$B$BRemember my words, $C, and do not fail.' WHERE entry=24743;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Fantastic. Help is exactly what I need.' WHERE entry=24792;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='That a weapon of such power has been redeemed from the clutches of evil is a great omen in these times, $N. With Quel\'Delar and staunch Silver Covenant allies at our side, the Lich King will have good reason to fear.$B$BThe crusade maintains an arsenal of exceptional weapons for our strongest allies. Allow me to offer you your choice from among them in return for entrusting us with the care of Quel\'Delar.' WHERE entry=24795;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='This is nothing short of an amazing accomplishment, $N. The day that Thalorien and Anasterian fell, the same day that Quel\'Delar was lost, was one of the darkest of my life. To see Quel\'Delar restored... it is beyond words.$B$BWithout a doubt, you are meant to be the true bearer of the blade. Quel\'Delar\'s magic is already adapting the blade to your skills and your strengths.' WHERE entry=24796;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Quel\'Delar rises again, as we sin\'dorei have risen from the ashes of defeat and betrayal. The heart and the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker are both with you, $N.$B$BI see the blade has already started adapting itself to your strengths, $N. Hold your head high and always keep Quel\'Delar at your side.' WHERE entry=24800;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Quel\'Delar rises again, as the sin\'dorei have risen from the ashes of defeat and betrayal. Yet, somehow, the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker has chosen to serve an outsider.$B$BBe at ease, $N. I do not mean to diminish your accomplishment, for you have done what none of my brothers could, although I do not know why. You are clearly meant to be its bearer; the blade is already adapting itself to your abilities. Wield Quel\'Delar proudly against our common foes.' WHERE entry=24801;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yet again, vengeance slips through my grasp. It\'s hard to believe how much stronger he\'s gotten.$B$BIt was foolish of you to come for me, but it\'s good to know that there are still some champions of the Horde that aren\'t useless cowards. The information Uther gave us may well be key to finally killing Arthas, though it is becoming more and more clear that the Horde will not be able to accomplish this on their own.$B$BGo, $C. I expect your prowess may be needed again very soon.' WHERE entry=24802;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Don\'t just stand there! Give me the shark and I\'ll declare you the winner!' WHERE entry=24803;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I\'m afraid we\'ve already had a winner for today, young $N. However, if you bring a shark, I\'ll see that it\'s released back into the waters, and I might just have a little something for you...' WHERE entry=24806;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='To atone for the sins I committed as one of the Lich King\'s Death Knights, I\'ve dedicated myself to creating rings of great power for our brothers and sisters to use in the struggle.$B$BYou\'ve proven yourself as a valuable ally in the fight against the Scourge, $N. As your dedication continues I can improve on the ring\'s original design.$B$BChoose your path carefully. A change of heart will come at a price.' WHERE entry=24815;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='May you find what you\'re looking for, $Gbrother:sister;.' WHERE entry=24819;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='May you find what you\'re looking for, $Gbrother:sister;.' WHERE entry=24820;
