UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Not another one! $N, these devices have been springing up all around Azeroth. We know that they can instigate elemental disturbances in the area, including causing tears in the elemental planes. The devices stink of Twilight\'s Hammer.  The engravings covering the surface and the captured elemental essence implicate Cho\'gall and his minions are behind this. If you find more of these, please bring them to me or one of my associates. We need to learn more about what\'s behind this attack!' WHERE entry=25570;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yes, $N, this shard does explain the occurrence of the rifts.  The elemental planes have been in chaos in Outland ever since Draenor was destroyed. These shards cause a weakness in the already damaged elemental planes and allow the elementals to cross over. We\'re still collecting information on who or what is behind all of this.  However, the more shards you bring me, the better prepared we will be to fight the elemental invasion here in Azeroth.' WHERE entry=25571;
