UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Yes, $N, this shard does explain the occurrence of the rift.  The elemental planes have been in chaos in Outland ever since Draenor was destroyed. These shards cause a weakness in the already damaged elemental planes and allow the elementals to cross into our world We\'re still looking into how these rifts are appearing in Azeroth.  Keep bringing us the shards.  Every shard we get brings us closer to understanding how these rifts are appearing.' WHERE entry=25773;
