UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Sandfury trolls and the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer, you say? And they meant to send some giant monster into the heart of the city?! Well done! Stormwind is in your debt.' WHERE entry=26054;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Sandfury trolls and the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer, you say? And they meant to send some giant monster into the heart of the city?! Well done! Thunder Bluff is in your debt.' WHERE entry=26990;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, ye say? At the behest of the Cult o\' Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Ironforge is in yer debt.' WHERE entry=27122;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, you say? At the behest of the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Orgrimmar is in your debt.' WHERE entry=27127;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='A massive prince of the wind, you say? The herald of Al\'Akir, the Windlord? Madness. All of it. Stormwind is in your debt, hero.' WHERE entry=27207;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='A massive prince of the wind, you say? The herald of Al\'Akir, the Windlord? Madness. All of it. All of Thunder Bluff is in your debt, $C.' WHERE entry=27209;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I\'m glad you\'ve come, $C.  These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get.' WHERE entry=27307;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='I\'m glad you\'ve come, $C.  These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get.' WHERE entry=27308;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='It is good that you\'ve come, $N.  We need all the help we can get with the situation here.' WHERE entry=27473;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Well met, $C.  I am Gavan Grayfeather, emissary of the Wildhammer shaman. There is much work to be done.  The leaders fear for their citizens, as many have turned to cults.  We shaman are concerned with the elemental unrest. Our advice to you, $C, is to be vigilant.  Help where you can, be it calming the people or putting the elementals at rest.  There is plenty to do.' WHERE entry=27540;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='King\'s honor, $C.  I am Captain Anton.  I am leading the investigation into the cultists that have appeared in Stormwind.' WHERE entry=27546;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='It is good to see you, $N.  Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth.' WHERE entry=27566;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Greetings, $C.  The situation here is tense.  The elements are restless and the people are scared and confused.  The Warchief is trying to find a semblance of balance between leading the people and protecting Azeroth.  Though it seems he will soon be leaving us to travel to Nagrand and gain insight about the elementals. Regardless of the Warchief\'s choice, we still must do what we can.  Help calm the populace, scour the lands for rogue elementals.  These tasks will surely help our cause.' WHERE entry=27570;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='It is good to see you, $C.  Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth.' WHERE entry=27572;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='So there were more cultists waiting to be admitted to the city? It\'s a good thing that you caught them, $N. Reading over the note that you found, it seems they\'re planning something big.' WHERE entry=27741;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='Excellent work, $N. The note you captured makes sense in light of this ritual the infiltrators mentioned. This city is infested with cultists and their sympathizers. We must act before their plans can come to fruition.' WHERE entry=27749;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You need to familiarize yourself with the portal ritual quickly. We need to send as many teams into Stormwind as we can. They\'re discovering and arresting more of our brothers each day.' WHERE entry=27767;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve done an excellent job tracking down and combating the cultists, but I fear they are right about one thing. We will never know if we\'ve gotten them all.' WHERE entry=27780;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You\'ve brought many of these traitors to justice, $N, and yet their numbers keep growing. I fear we won\'t be able to stomp out all these rituals in time...' WHERE entry=27799;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='You need to familiarize yourself with the portal ritual quickly. We\'ve sent dozens of brothers into the city, but only so many can evade capture. We\'re relying on you, $N.' WHERE entry=27800;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='So there were more cultists waiting to be admitted to the city? It\'s a good thing that you caught them, $N. Reading over the note that you found, it seems they\'re planning something big.' WHERE entry=27801;
UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc2='So they\'re preparing some kind of ritual all over the city? Orgrimmar city is infested with cultists and their sympathizers and the warchief is at wit\'s end. We must do something!' WHERE entry=27802;

